<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-every-day">1.★ <strong>每日；天天；常常 (every day)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Experts say that 20 minutes of walking daily can make you feel less anxious.
